        "id": "term1",
        "label": "Term 1",
        "default": "<b>Qualified Referral.</b> A Qualified Referral is defined as a purchase made at Sheertex.com by a person (a 'Referred Customer') who arrives at our website by clicking your Refer-a-Friend program link, makes a payment for an order of $50+, and receives the goods and/or services purchased. You are limited to one Qualified Referral for each Referred Customer; in other words, additional/repeat purchases made by a Referred Customer are not counted as additional Qualified Referrals and you will not receive a referral reward on any additional/repeat purchases."
