        "type": "html",
        "id": "term2",
        "label": "Term 2",
        "default": "<b>Referred Customer.</b> The Referred Customer and the Referrer cannot be the same person (for example, by using a different email address)."
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "term3",
        "label": "Term 3",
        "default": "<b>Referral Rewards.</b> For you to earn referral rewards as a Referrer, the Referred Customer must access our website through your Refer-a-Friend program link, have made a payment for an order of $50+, and received the goods and/or services from Sheertex."
