        "id": "term4",
        "label": "Term 4",
        "default": "<b>Reward Payments.</b> For each Qualified Referral, the Referrer will earn one referral reward which is  payable in the form  of a $20 Single Use Coupon off an order of $50+ from Sheertex.com. Additional terms and conditions apply to this offer. See “Offer terms” below. As a Referrer, you are responsible for any and all tax liability resulting from Referral Rewards."
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "term5",
        "label": "Term 5",
        "default": "<b>Eligibility.</b> Eligibility is limited to individuals only. Sheertex’s Refer-a-Friend Program cannot be used by businesses for affiliate lead generation as determined in Sheertex’s sole discretion. (Corporations are not people, my friend!)"
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "term6",
        "label": "Term 6",
        "default": "<b>No Spam.</b> You must comply with all privacy and anti-spam laws. You must ensure that you only refer individuals with whom you have a personal or family relationship, and who would want to receive the referral email.  We will send your Friend(s) an email with information on how to obtain the reward on your behalf. You may refer a maximum of [25] friends in total. Emails must be created and distributed in a personal manner and bulk email distribution, distribution to strangers, or individuals with whom you do not have a personal or family relationship is prohibited and may be grounds for immediate termination and further legal action. Any distribution of your referral link that could constitute unsolicited commercial email or 'spam' under any applicable law or regulation is expressly prohibited and will be grounds for immediate termination of your account and exclusion from Sheertex’s Refer-a-Friend program. By submitting any email address as part of the Program, the Referrer represents that he/she: (i) has the appropriate permission and consent of the email recipient; (ii) is only sending the email to individuals with whom the Referrer has a personal or family relationship; and (iii)  is not engaging in harassing, unethical, illegal or otherwise improper conduct.  Bulk email distribution."
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "term7",
        "label": "Term 7",
        "default": "<b>Right to Close Accounts.</b> Sheertex reserves the right to close the account(s) of any Referrer and/or Referred Customer and to request proper payment if the Referrer and/or Referred Customer attempts to use the Sheertex Refer-a-Friend program in a questionable manner or breaches any of these Terms & Conditions or is in violation of any law, statute or governmental regulation."
      },{
        "type": "html",
        "id": "term8",
        "label": "Term 8",
        "default": "<b>Right to Cancel Program or Change Terms.</b> Except where prohibited by applicable law (which may include the Province of Quebec), Sheertex reserves the right to cancel the Refer-a-Friend Program or to change these Terms & Conditions at any time in its sole discretion and any unclaimed referral rewards will be forfeited at that time."
      }
    ]
  }
